</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="title page">
<PB REF="2">
<P>THE ATHENAID, A POEM,</P>
<P>BY THE AUTHOR OF LEONIDAS.</P>
<P>VOL. II.</P>
<P>LONDON: PRINTED FOR T. CADELL, IN THE STRAND. M.DCC.LXXXVII.</P>
